# ACCESS CONTROL LIST (ACL) NOTES===
-OBJECT OWNWERSHIP MUST GIVE THEN ONLY CAN GIVE ACL TO BOTH BUCKET + OBJECT LEVEL PERMIAIIONS
-OLD METHOD NOT USED
-FOR GIVING ACL OR BUCKET POLICY ABOVE A1 SETTING NEED TO CHANGE AS PER NEED SO FOR THIS CHANGE 1ST/2ND ACL UNBLOCKING FROM ABOVE THRN ONLY U CAN CHANHE 
1-NEW ACL BLOCK
2-ALL ACL ACCESSS BLOCK

# BUCKET POLICY USE====
3-NEW POLICY BLOCK
4-ALL POLICY BLOCK

{
    "Version": "2012-10-17",
    "Statement": [
        {
            "Sid": "PublicReadGetObject",
            "Effect": "Allow",
            "Principal": "*",
            "Action": "s3:GetObject",
            "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::your-bucket-name/*"
        }
    ]
}


